## Supabase Setup

Make sure your Supabase table `waitlist_emails` has the correct RLS policy:

```sql
-- Allow public inserts
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Allow public inserts" ON waitlist_emails;
CREATE POLICY "Allow public inserts" ON waitlist_emails FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (true);
```
